The cute princess Rapunzel has got the invitation from a prom party that is going to take place in the nearby fantasy forest. All other princesses like Anna, Elsa, Ariel, Jasmine, Snow White, and Cinderella are coming there in their chosen style. However, Rapunzel has chosen today the style of Winx. Although she carries a wide collection of outfits in this style, you valuable fashion advice could help her find a unique dressing style. Will you be her friend in sorting out the puzzle? Join Rapunzel Princess Winx Style and be prepared to help her get an eye-catching look!

It is always important to be well dressed up to be available at the ball event. Everyone tries her best to look fabulous for such kind of party. Your favorite princess also has a desire of wearing a stand-out dress on that occasion. Mix and match as many outfit and accessory options as you can to create a look that could help stand her out from the crowd in this brand new dressing game! There are plenty of options in tops, bottoms, shoes, fairy wings and other accessories. 

Do not forget to combine her look with a matching hairstyle in this html5 dress up game. In every category, you will find out six options to explore. You can try them all to decide which look can actually provide her a grace she deserves for. Your lovely efforts can help the lady to spot her dreamy prince in the ball. All the best to dress her up in the optimum possible way and have fun, no download required on atmegame.com!
